  <!-- ## Description & History -->

  <!-- Describe your product here. Be brief. -->
  <description>
    EMUUROM is a nonviolent creature-scanning exploration platformer, where you document an ancient paradise before it's lost forever.
    EMUUROM is a rule-discovery game ("metroidbrainia") in the vein of Animal Well, Void Stranger and Tunic: knowledge opens new paths.
    Equipped with a unique SCANNER BEAM, you reveal hidden pathways and study the EMUUROM creatures to gain knowledge and create new paths forward.
    The environmental puzzles range from obvious to obscure, with a plethora of secrets hidden in plain sight:
    this creates a multi-layered experience for many kinds of players.
    As you gain a better understanding on the world around you, the machinations of the EMUUROM creatures begin to unfold...


  </description>

  <!--
    Tell the story of your product with the `<history>` tag.
